The paper discusses the use of statistical inference in citation analysis, which is a topic related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper touches on issues related to cybernetics (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and cryptography and security (cs.CR) as they relate to citation analysis.
